{
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Sympy: Symbolic Computing {#sec-sympy}\n",
        "\n",
        "$~$\n",
        "\n",
        "[![](https://www.sympy.org/static/images/logo.png)](https://docs.sympy.org/latest/index.html)\n",
        "\n",
        "$~$\n",
        "\n",
        "## Importing sympy\n"
      ],
      "id": "c6cfc729"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "import sympy\n",
        "from sympy import I, pi, oo\n",
        "sympy.init_printing()\n",
        "\n",
        "from IPython.display import display\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"sympy: \", sympy.__version__)"
      ],
      "id": "a1bbf6ce",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Symbols\n"
      ],
      "id": "7708b998"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = sympy.Symbol('x')\n",
        "print(x.is_real)"
      ],
      "id": "2c412d60",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "y = sympy.Symbol('y', real=True)\n",
        "y.is_real"
      ],
      "id": "66c1684c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "z = sympy.Symbol('z', complex=True)\n",
        "z.is_complex"
      ],
      "id": "799b877f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "print(z.is_real)"
      ],
      "id": "dc245845",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "16807008"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = sympy.Symbol('x')\n",
        "y = sympy.Symbol('y', positive=True)\n",
        "z = sympy.Symbol('z', negative=True)"
      ],
      "id": "0e695b60",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.sqrt(x**2)"
      ],
      "id": "b5fb13ec",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.sqrt(y**2)"
      ],
      "id": "e1b59e57",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.sqrt(z**2)"
      ],
      "id": "b75bd3ae",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "0ddf559c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "n1 = sympy.Symbol('n')\n",
        "n2 = sympy.Symbol('n', integer=True)\n",
        "n3 = sympy.Symbol('n', odd=True)\n",
        "n4 = sympy.Symbol('n', even=True)"
      ],
      "id": "fa9eaf8c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.cos(n1*pi)"
      ],
      "id": "e95cb693",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.cos(n2*pi)"
      ],
      "id": "5ccc7a0d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.cos(n3*pi)"
      ],
      "id": "94d91593",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.cos(n4*pi)"
      ],
      "id": "043862ba",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "b615a6b1"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a, b, c = sympy.symbols('a, b, c', negative=True)"
      ],
      "id": "fbb9ab45",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "d, e, f = sympy.symbols('d, e, f', positive=True)"
      ],
      "id": "3a48b28a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Numbers\n",
        "\n",
        "* We cannot directly use the built-in Python objects for integers, `int`, and floating-point numbers, `float`, and so on. Instead, `sympy` provides the classes `sympy.Integer` and `sympy.Float` for representing integers and floating-point numbers within the `sympy` framework\n",
        "\n",
        "* This distinction is important to be aware of when working with `sympy`, but fortunately we rarely\n",
        "need to concern ourselves with creating objects of type `sympy.Integer` and `sympy.Float` to representing\n",
        "specific numbers, $~$since `sympy` automatically promotes Python numbers to instances of these classes when they occur in `sympy` expressions\n"
      ],
      "id": "44e978a9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "i = sympy.Integer(18)\n",
        "type(i)"
      ],
      "id": "12afa90a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "i.is_Integer, i.is_real, i.is_odd, i.is_even"
      ],
      "id": "4b4fe835",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f = sympy.Float(2.3)\n",
        "type(f)"
      ],
      "id": "d0e01110",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f.is_Float, f.is_real, f.is_complex"
      ],
      "id": "0f0395be",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "44cc1d7a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "i, f = sympy.sympify(19), sympy.sympify(2.3)\n",
        "type(i), type(f)"
      ],
      "id": "a2e32b79",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Integer \n",
        "\n",
        "* While the `Symbol` with `integer=True` represents some integer, $\\,$the `Integer` instance represents a\n",
        "specific integer\n",
        "\n",
        "* For both cases, $\\,$the `is_integer` attribute is `True`, $\\,$but there is also an attribute `is_Integer`\n",
        "(note the capital `I`), $\\,$which is only `True` for `Integer` instances\n"
      ],
      "id": "7e9cf64a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "n = sympy.Symbol('n', integer=True)\n",
        "n.is_integer, n.is_Integer, n.is_positive, n.is_Symbol"
      ],
      "id": "caa1c70b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "i = sympy.Integer(19)\n",
        "i.is_integer, i.is_Integer, i.is_positive, i.is_Symbol"
      ],
      "id": "0d5ac2a4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.Integer('19' *20)"
      ],
      "id": "2076697d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.Integer('12_345_678'), sympy.Integer(12_345_678)"
      ],
      "id": "d83e94dd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# great common division, leat common multiple\n",
        "sympy.igcd(36, 15), sympy.ilcm(7, 34)"
      ],
      "id": "06ca4f0c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* Integers in `sympy` are <font color='red'>**arbitrary precision**</font>, $\\,$meaning that they have <font color='blue'>no fixed lower and upper bounds</font>,\n",
        "$\\,$which is the case when representing integers with a specific bit-size, as, for example, in `numpy`\n"
      ],
      "id": "ccfda2d9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "i = sympy.Integer(19)\n",
        "i**100"
      ],
      "id": "86baaf7c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.factorial(100)"
      ],
      "id": "a8398ff0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Float\n",
        "\n",
        "* Like `Integer`, $\\,$`Float` is <font color='red'>**arbitrary precision**</font>, $\\,$in contrast to Python’s built-in `float` type and the `float` types in `numpy`. $\\,$This means that any `Float` can represent a `float` with arbitrary number of decimals\n",
        "\n",
        "* When a `Float` instance is created using its constructor, $\\,$there are two arguments: the first argument is **a Python `float` or a string representing a floating-point number**, and the second (optional) argument is the **precision** (number of significant decimal digits) of the `Float` object\n"
      ],
      "id": "ba11d591"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# create a string representation with 25 decimals\n",
        "f'{0.3:.25f}'  "
      ],
      "id": "e80a868d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.Float(0.3, 25) "
      ],
      "id": "a85d6b14",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.Float('0.3', 25)"
      ],
      "id": "67e69c5e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.Float('123 456 789.123_456', '')"
      ],
      "id": "4958f2d1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Rational\n"
      ],
      "id": "cbb92728"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "r0 = sympy.Rational(11, 13)\n",
        "r0"
      ],
      "id": "1739623b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "r0.p, r0.q"
      ],
      "id": "d98fc246",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "r1 = sympy.Rational(2, 3)\n",
        "r2 = sympy.Rational(4, 5)"
      ],
      "id": "bbd1a5f6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "r1 * r2"
      ],
      "id": "f1f2445e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "r1 / r2"
      ],
      "id": "421fe93d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.Rational(0.2), sympy.Rational('0.2')"
      ],
      "id": "1cee71b3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Constants and special symbols\n",
        "\n",
        "$\\displaystyle \\gamma = \\lim_{n \\to \\infty} \\left( \\sum_{k=1}^n \\frac{1}{k} -\\ln n\\right)$\n"
      ],
      "id": "f222b070"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.pi, sympy.E, sympy.EulerGamma, sympy.I, sympy.oo"
      ],
      "id": "4136a302",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Functions\n"
      ],
      "id": "6fde2483"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x, y, z = sympy.symbols('x, y, z')"
      ],
      "id": "b49c24b7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f = sympy.Function('f')\n",
        "type(f)"
      ],
      "id": "412953aa",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f(x)"
      ],
      "id": "10361ef4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "g = sympy.Function('g')(x, y, z)\n",
        "g"
      ],
      "id": "b08151e7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "g.free_symbols"
      ],
      "id": "f6e85fb8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "a5869047"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.sin"
      ],
      "id": "54f5e7e4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.sin(x)"
      ],
      "id": "754b3f16",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.sin(pi *1.5)"
      ],
      "id": "f04d2911",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "n = sympy.Symbol('n', integer=True)\n",
        "sympy.sin(pi * n)"
      ],
      "id": "e1785cf9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "h = sympy.Lambda(x, x**2)\n",
        "h"
      ],
      "id": "8e32f10b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "h(5)"
      ],
      "id": "45ae4991",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "h(1 + x)"
      ],
      "id": "af483af5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Expressions\n"
      ],
      "id": "9c6294ea"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = sympy.Symbol('x')\n",
        "\n",
        "expr = 1 +2*x**2 +3*x**3\n",
        "expr"
      ],
      "id": "71e1f548",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.args"
      ],
      "id": "1eda21ff",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.args[2]"
      ],
      "id": "d0ade085",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.args[2].args"
      ],
      "id": "b102ea64",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.args[2].args[1]"
      ],
      "id": "c4e622ee",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.args[2].args[1].args"
      ],
      "id": "3ce7b6bb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.args[2].args[1].args[1]"
      ],
      "id": "8697ae47",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.args[2].args[1].args[1].args"
      ],
      "id": "17ef0b35",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Manipulating expressions\n",
        "\n",
        "### Simplication\n"
      ],
      "id": "08bb9acf"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr = 2 * (x**2 - x) - x * (x + 1)\n",
        "expr"
      ],
      "id": "f21e01de",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.simplify(expr)"
      ],
      "id": "6a3e2117",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.simplify()"
      ],
      "id": "10b357e1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr"
      ],
      "id": "717bb4b1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "9bed4924"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr = 2 * sympy.cos(x) * sympy.sin(x)\n",
        "expr"
      ],
      "id": "b6b90cc9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.simplify(expr)"
      ],
      "id": "2c8c9e0b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr = sympy.exp(x) * sympy.exp(y)\n",
        "expr"
      ],
      "id": "b0184203",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.simplify(expr)"
      ],
      "id": "67af0bd5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Expand\n"
      ],
      "id": "4abb6aff"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr = (x + 1) * (x + 2)\n",
        "expr"
      ],
      "id": "95f92d82",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.expand()"
      ],
      "id": "5b3bb81f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "b0a06c62"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.sin(x + y).expand(trig=True)"
      ],
      "id": "9d0938f4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a, b = sympy.symbols('a, b', positive=True)\n",
        "sympy.log(a * b).expand(log=True)"
      ],
      "id": "27bc6d43",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.exp(I*a + b).expand(complex=True)"
      ],
      "id": "abb073dc",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.expand((a * b)**x, power_base=True)"
      ],
      "id": "375f1e1f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.exp(I*(a -b)*x).expand(power_exp=True)"
      ],
      "id": "55e5843c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Factor, collect and combine\n"
      ],
      "id": "798da3c7"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.factor(x**2 - 1)"
      ],
      "id": "7cc3e879",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.factor(x *sympy.cos(y) + x *sympy.sin(z))"
      ],
      "id": "d77d5831",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "547e657e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr = x + y + x * y * z\n",
        "expr"
      ],
      "id": "168159c8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.collect(x)"
      ],
      "id": "df3e1338",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr.collect(y)"
      ],
      "id": "4a46bf04",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "7ea59e22"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr = sympy.cos(x + y) + sympy.sin(x - y)"
      ],
      "id": "55bba526",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr1 = expr.expand(trig=True)\n",
        "expr1"
      ],
      "id": "6961f9a6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr2 = expr1.collect([sympy.cos(x), sympy.sin(x)])\n",
        "expr2"
      ],
      "id": "1d35d920",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr3 = expr2.collect(sympy.cos(y) - sympy.sin(y))\n",
        "expr3"
      ],
      "id": "28e7bfbb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "192a9647"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.logcombine(sympy.log(a) - sympy.log(b))"
      ],
      "id": "c36f5576",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Apart, together and cancel\n"
      ],
      "id": "2b762047"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr1 = 1/(x**2 + 3*x + 2)\n",
        "expr1"
      ],
      "id": "30cd9956",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.apart(expr1, x)"
      ],
      "id": "e24fbfab",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr2 = 1 / (y * x + y) + 1 / (1+x)\n",
        "expr2"
      ],
      "id": "1a8026e8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.together(expr2)"
      ],
      "id": "d9cf6837",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "expr3 = y / (y * x + y)\n",
        "expr3"
      ],
      "id": "cebfaa51",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "sympy.cancel(expr3)"
      ],
      "id": "63fe161c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
